y]]\t\n|[[Green Bay Packers]]\n|E\n|-\n|1937\t\n|6\t\n|8\t\n|58\t\n|[[Del Bjork]]\t\n|[[Chicago Bears]]\t\n|T\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|1936\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|2\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|9\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|18\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|[[Tuffy Leemans]]\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|[[New York Giants]]\n| align=\"center\" bgcolor=#D0E7FF|FB\n|-\n|5\t\n|5\t\n|41\t\n|[[Stan Riordan]]\t\n|[[Chicago Cardinals]]\t\n|E\n|- \t\n|8\t\n|6\t\n|69\t\n|[[Ross Carter]]\t\n|[[Chicago Cardinals]]\t\n|G\n|-\n|}\n\n<ref>[http://www.drafthistory.com/index.php/colleges/o DraftHistory.com]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Oregon Ducks football navbox}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of National Football League draftees by college football team|Oregon]]\n[[Category:Oregon Ducks football players|*]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis is a '''list of [[Oregon Ducks football]] players in the NFL Draft.'''\n\n==Key==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| B\n| Back\n| K\n| [[Placekicker|Kicker]]\n| NT\n| [[Nose tackle]]\n|-\n| C\n| [[Center (American football)|Center]]\n| LB\n| [[Linebacker]]\n| FB\n| [[Fullback (American football)|Fullback]]\n|-\n| DB\n| [[Defensive back]]\n| P\n| [[Punter (American football)|Punter]]\n| HB\n| [[Halfback (American football)|Halfback]]\n|-\n| DE\n| [[Defensive end]]\n| QB\n| [[Quarterback]]\n| WR\n| [[Wide receiver]]\n|-\n| DT\n| [[Defensive tackle]]\n| RB\n| [[Running back]]\n| G\n| [[Guard (American football)|Guard]]\n|-\n| E\n| [[End (American football)|End]]\n| T\n| [[Offensive tackle]]\n| TE\n| [[Tight end]]\n|-\n|}\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n | style=\"background-color:#FFE6BD\" align=\"center\" | <sup>*</sup>\n | colspan=\"5\" | Selected to an all-star game ([[American Football League All-Star game|AFL All-Star game]], [[Pro Bowl#NFL All-Star Games (1939\u20131942)|NFL All-Star game]] or [[Pro Bowl]])\n|-\n | style=\"background-color:#DDFFDD\" align=\"center\" | <sup>{{dagger